			<p class="bolded2">Patented Technology</p>
			<p class="p4">Brain.fm holds patents on key processes for creating functional music, including technology to elicit strong neural phase locking-allowing populations of neurons to engage in various kinds of coordinated activity-and technology to remove distraction in sound.</p>
			<p class="p5">This makes our music unique, purpose-built to steer you into a desired mental state. In other words, we've found new ways to create music that helps you do what you need to do. </p>
