			<p class="bolded3">Tested on Brain and Behavior</p>
			<p class="p7">Scientists at Brain.fm work with collaborators at academic institutions to run experiements.</p>
			<p class="p8">We look at the effects of our technology on the brain, using fMRI and EEG, and also run large-scale behavioral tests, measuring performance on simple games.</p>
			<p class="p9">Our experiments always include a control condition("placebo") of the same underlying music without brain.fm technology applied, so we can be sure our tech is what makes the difference.</p>
